# 🚀 Mallikarjun Malli - Portfolio Website

A modern, responsive portfolio website showcasing my skills, projects, and professional experience in web development, AI/ML, and software engineering.

## ✨ Features

- **🌓 Dark/Light Theme Toggle** - Seamless theme switching with localStorage persistence
- **📱 Fully Responsive Design** - Optimized for all screen sizes and devices
- **🎨 Modern UI/UX** - Glass-morphism effects, gradients, and smooth animations
- **📧 Contact Form Integration** - EmailJS powered contact form sending emails directly to Gmail
- **🎯 Smooth Animations** - CSS animations, skill progress bars, and scroll effects
- **⚡ Fast Performance** - Optimized loading and modern web technologies
- **🔗 Social Media Integration** - Direct links to LinkedIn, GitHub, and other platforms

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

### Frontend
- **HTML5** - Semantic markup and accessibility features
- **CSS3** - Modern styling with custom properties, flexbox, and grid
- **JavaScript ES6+** - Interactive functionality and DOM manipulation
- **FontAwesome** - Professional icon library

### Services & APIs
- **EmailJS** - Frontend email service integration
- **Google Fonts** - Professional typography (Poppins, Inter)

### Development Tools
- **Git & GitHub** - Version control and repository hosting
- **VS Code** - Development environment
- **PowerShell** - Terminal and command line operations

## 📋 Project Structure

```
Portfolio/
├── index.html          # Main HTML file with semantic structure
├── style.css           # Complete CSS styling with theme system
├── script.js           # JavaScript functionality and EmailJS integration
├── me2.jpg            # Profile image
├── .env               # EmailJS credentials (not committed to git)
└── readme             # Project documentation
```

## 🎨 Design Features

### Color Scheme
- **Primary**: Modern gradients with purple and blue tones
- **Dark Theme**: Professional dark backgrounds with accent colors
- **Light Theme**: Clean white backgrounds with subtle shadows

