## 🔧 Customization

### Theme Colors
Update CSS custom properties in `style.css`:
```css
:root {
  --primary-color: #667eea;
  --secondary-color: #764ba2;
  --accent-color: #f093fb;
}
```

### Content Updates
- Update personal information in `index.html`
- Replace profile image (`me2.jpg`)
- Modify projects and skills sections

